name: Flying the DASH 8-400 with AIR CANADA EXPRESS! Calgary to Regina (4K)
description:
The Dash 8-400 is easily the most popular regional airliner in Canada, but I haven't actually flown on it with Air Canada Express - until now!

Here's the story of what turned out to be quite an interesting flight from Calgary to Regina.
